{"tid":1155706,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【本土研究社又贏】成就獲得：你再次解封8份港英時代機密檔案","createTime":"2019-05-15T06:28:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-15T14:21:43.000Z","uid":138409,"like":60,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"dc57b738e1bdb9ac25f63645eb3326d0f3bb3577","tid":1155706,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T06:28:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/decodinghkhistory/posts/1261207114033249\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fdecodinghkhistory%2Fposts%2F1261207114033249&d=UmPnmdD3xn3sHJtz75hgV0v%2FgUeHX8FRhdV3zHjzpFI%3D&h=cfc75414\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/decodinghkhistory/posts/1261207114033249</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/usM7wYJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FusM7wYJ.jpg&h=e1e826d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wapwYDK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwapwYDK.jpg&h=48a24930&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/74o2kR5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F74o2kR5.jpg&h=ce2b17df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7joqiDL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7joqiDL.jpg&h=1add328d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當年有政黨成功爭取「北極有企鵝」，可以話係一大「政績」；香港前途研究計劃最近都成功爭取呀，不過係真正既重要成果，因為又有多份與香港命運攸關嘅密檔重見天日啦！<br />\n<br />\n英國宜家有超過1000份有關香港的檔案俾英國政府封鎖到2049年，香港前途研究計劃一直透過《資訊自由法》上訴封鎖決定，希望打破「2049年期限」提早解封，實行「還檔於民」。<br />\n<br />\n苦苦堅持，梗係有意義啦。香港前途研究計劃今次成功解封嘅檔案數目大增，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">半年內成功爭取至少8份英國密檔，份份原本2049年都係先開封，但宜家就提早30年出土，而且份份都涉及各大重要議題，包括特首權限、城規條例修訂等。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n當中一份個名係「Political activism: accusations of subversion in Hong Kong」（<span style=\"color: gold;\">政治行動主義：指控香港的顛覆行為</span>），檔案年期是六四翌年、1990年建立，估計同當年大陸當局「屈」香港支援六四活動是顛覆活動有關；另一份就涉及90年代初香港《公安條例》修訂，估計就係講當年取消遊行示威「註冊制度」，放寬對集會自由管制。<br />\n<br />\n正值宜家「送中條例」爭議，我地都「相當心急、好心急、非常心急」，<span style=\"color: gold;\">今年初已經要求提早解封「後八九」引渡相關檔案，其中包括「Hong Kong: extradition; future aspects」及「Hong Kong: extradition matters」，對方最近4月底已經回信，話做緊公眾利益測試 (Public Interest Test) 啦</span>，希望好快就可以提早解封，到時就可以呈現當年討論，等林鄭唔可以一句「廢話」玩香港人。<br />\n<br />\n想知今次成功爭取咗啲咩，可以埋嚟睇、埋嚟揀👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻：<br />\n<br />\nFCO 40/1762: Future of Hong Kong: White Paper on the Joint Declaration<br />\n<br />\nFCO 40/1931 Executive Council of Hong Kong: memoranda and minutes of meetings<br />\n<br />\nFCO 40/2845: Sensitivity review of Hong Kong Government records<br />\n<br />\nFCO 40/2861: Hong Kong constitutional development: Chief Executive<br />\n<br />\nFCO 40/2932: Political activism: accusations of subversion in Hong Kong<br />\n<br />\nFCO 40/2952: Hong Kong: Town Planning (Amendment) Bill 1990<br />\n<br />\nFCO 40/3188: Future of Hong Kong: Public Order Ordinance<br />\n<br />\nFCO 40/3189: Constitutional development in Hong Kong: role of the Legislative Council<br />\n<br />\n相關貼文：<br />\n香港前途研究計劃衝出國際<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2Yud3fE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Yud3fE&d=UmPnmdD3xn3sHJtz75hgV0v%2FgUeHX8FRhdV3zHjzpFI%3D&h=d7182b96\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2Yud3fE</a> <br />\n───────"},{"pid":"4db375b95879a075a8a879858181b689fb6faf07","tid":1155706,"uid":138409,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T06:29:06.000Z","msg":"前途研究計劃（前研）响 medium 梳理咗送中條例系列文章，請大家 follow 與 claps（可以每篇文拍 50 吓手），<span style=\"color: gold;\">每下掌聲都會化作前研嘅收入來源，請畀多啲掌聲研究員 </span>👏👏👏<br />\n◤反送中系列◢<br />\n五）No agreement is better than a bad agreement <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2YhLmGS\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2YhLmGS&d=UmPnmdD3xn3sHJtz75hgV0v%2FgUeHX8FRhdV3zHjzpFI%3D&h=445d7571\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2YhLmGS</a><br />\n四）沒有中港區隔下的美港關係 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2LBdHGP\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2LBdHGP&d=UmPnmdD3xn3sHJtz75hgV0v%2FgUeHX8FRhdV3zHjzpFI%3D&h=a66b2501\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2LBdHGP</a><br />\n三）讓惡法多睡一會 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2Jf8Lpc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Jf8Lpc&d=UmPnmdD3xn3sHJtz75hgV0v%2FgUeHX8FRhdV3zHjzpFI%3D&h=a12dd009\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2Jf8Lpc</a><br />\n二）《逃犯條例》修訂「殺到埋身」<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2H9WYGi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2H9WYGi&d=UmPnmdD3xn3sHJtz75hgV0v%2FgUeHX8FRhdV3zHjzpFI%3D&h=13a23475\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2H9WYGi</a><br />\n一）立會反擊戰：林鄭的謊言 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2Jb6sDq\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Jb6sDq&d=UmPnmdD3xn3sHJtz75hgV0v%2FgUeHX8FRhdV3zHjzpFI%3D&h=46499bd9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2Jb6sDq</a><br />\n───────<br />\n█ 解密過去🔓重掌未來 █<br />\n💰捐款支持：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2IVW56L\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2IVW56L&d=UmPnmdD3xn3sHJtz75hgV0v%2FgUeHX8FRhdV3zHjzpFI%3D&h=382a2279\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2IVW56L</a><br />\n📖研究成果：<a href=\"https://medium.com/@decodinghkshistory\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2F%40decodinghkshistory&d=UmPnmdD3xn3sHJtz75hgV0v%2FgUeHX8FRhdV3zHjzpFI%3D&h=b8d36547\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://medium.com/@decodinghkshistory</a><br />\n🗂計劃詳情：<a href=\"https://researchforfuture.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresearchforfuture.hk&d=UmPnmdD3xn3sHJtz75hgV0v%2FgUeHX8FRhdV3zHjzpFI%3D&h=b6cc3019\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://researchforfuture.hk</a><br />\n📱instagram：<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/decodinghkshistory\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fdecodinghkshistory&d=UmPnmdD3xn3sHJtz75hgV0v%2FgUeHX8FRhdV3zHjzpFI%3D&h=fb582e36\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">ht